{{notability|Biographies|date=November 2015}}
'''Hussein Khaliqi''' or '''Huseyn Xelîqî''' or '''Hossein Khalighi''' or '''Ḥusayn Khalīqī''', is a contemporary [[Kurdish people|Kurdish]] writer. He was born in [[Iranian Kurdistan]]. He studied [[philosophy]], [[history]] and [[sociology]] in [[University of Tabriz]]. He is currently the head of the ''Kurdish Institute of Stockholm''.

